        <div class="section_div">
          <p class="content_text">This OTP is valid for only 10 minutes.</p>
          <p class="content_text">
            If you have further inquiries, please email us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@keble.co" class="content_link"
              >Hello@keble.co</a
            >
            and our support team will be right with you.
          </p>
          <p class="content_text">
            Thank you for choosing Keble to Save, Invest and Grow.
        </div>

        <div class="regard_div">
          <p class="regard_text">Best regards,</p>
          <p class="regard_text_bold">The Keble Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="button_sect">
          <button>
            <a
              href="https://apps.apple.com/ng/app/keble-global-real-estate/id6463791690"
